},{"user":{"name":"Peggy Osborne","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/102210227563171034444?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwi4iJ_Uxrj3AhWopXIEHaRWAvkQvvQBegUIARDAAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJwbwBqciY6vYKkaN-q3iXZlNBgCt7z_S6HY6kRe=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":2},"rating":5,"date":"a year ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"Michael and team are the best! Very thoughtful and courteous. Willing to take time to hear what their clients are looking for. Installation was very professional. BEAUTIFUL results with complete clean up. Could not be happier! Highly recommend!","likes":1,"response":{"date":"a year ago","snippet":"Peggy, we appreciate the compliment!"}},{"user":{"name":"Jennifer Miotke","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/103848078550460347575?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwi4iJ_Uxrj3AhWopXIEHaRWAvkQvvQBegUIARDPAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a-\/AOh14Gh1VxM1ziQVqHtq51rzyXE2-fn2opwrJBSh4hiCvg=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":4},"rating":5,"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Michael\'s team is quick professional and did a great job. I have hired him twice. Once to do a patio. It was sinking and they leveled it out. No problems at all a year later. The second time was to level the backyard so there was no potholes or puddles when it rained and pull up a couple dead trees. I thought it would take a week and it took two days. Everyone wore uniforms and they were on time, quick and efficient. I would always hire Michael now and always recommend him for landscaping needs.","likes":1,"response":{"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Thank you for your great review, Jennifer! We feel it\'s important to maintain a professional image for all of our jobs. Thanks for noticing! We\'re happy to hear you\'ve had a great experience with us! Thank you for choosing Michaelangelo\'s Sustainable Landscape & Design Group!"}},{"user":{"name":"James Errico","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/103113601744600372814?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiTqP_Vxrj3AhWTlWoFHYnnBhsQvvQBegQIARBB","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a-\/AOh14GiwYKf9oY3CCfZrNxfB2GUJmcT0NfeI-yAcrNJnmQ=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":13},"rating":4,"date":"a month ago","summary":"Positive: Punctuality, Quality","snippet":"Really enjoyed working with Michael (owner), Bruce (designer), and crew (Roberto and Mario). They were very knowledgeable, easy to work with, and accommodating. Work was done fast and looks great. I really appreciated their input at every step of the way to address things like modifying how the gate doors around to improve the design and function of the landscape. Mario was also very receptive to small changes that sometimes get lost between design and implementation. Originally given a 5 star, I\'ve since lowered it. 5 of my magnolia trees all died. No fault of mine or Michaelangelo\'s, so they were replaced. Without diving into details it was the poor communication that caused this drop in rating. I was told dates that would then pass without any communication and sometimes left wondering if I\'d been forgotten. After a heated conversation with an unmentioned employee both sides calmed down and the situation was resolved and I walked away very happy. The trees were replaced and I was very happy with the replacement. That said, the guys left after installing the replacement trees without even a goodbye or better yet asking if I was satisfied with the work. After spending ~$65k on this project I expected a little more courtesy during the warranty period. It\'s hard to give one rating for all involved so: Sales: 5 Design: 5 Implementation: 5 Warranty: 3 Services: Sod installation , Yard landscaping , Yard drainage , Hardscaping , Landscape design , Stone masonry","response":{"date":"a month ago","snippet":"We set a high standard for ourselves and are truly sorry to hear that standard was not met in your interaction with us. Please get in touch with us at (770) 940-4336 and we\'d be happy to help you out. Cheers, Michaelangelo\'s Sustainable Landscape & Design Group"}},{"user":{"name":"Gretchen Fletcher","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/112131243224078488457?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiTqP_Vxrj3AhWTlWoFHYnnBhsQvvQBegQIARBX","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJxBMvJBWW3Bl2al6RMwINvdRiUyYag2nbh5tU0a=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":1},"rating":5,"date":"5 months ago","snippet":"Michaelangelo\'s is fantastic! I cannot say enough about their customer service, not to mention the actual landscaping is beautiful! To start, a specialist came to our location and hand drew a landscaping design. From there, it was a very simple process. Not only did they install a beautiful landscape to our property, they were also able to connect us with other companies to assist with other projects that has nothing to even do with the landscape. The owner is amazing and extremely responsive. Everyone I encountered with the company was professional and knowledgeable. You can tell they are very passionate about what they do, and will do whatever it takes to make sure their customers are satisfied! Highly recommend! Service: Custom masonry","likes":1,"response":{"date":"5 months ago","snippet":"Thank you, Gretchen! Glad we could provide great service!"}},{"user":{"name":"rachel macon","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/112008221700785643384?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiTqP_Vxrj3AhWTlWoFHYnnBhsQvvQBegQIARBl","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a-\/AOh14GhTar5jV10VYzgBlBY4eU6XUTt6lOQhFzMAfNv-2w=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":11,"photos":1},"rating":5,"date":"2 months ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"Michaelangelo\'s did a FANTASTIC job landscaping our yard. We only did our first phase with them and look forward to hiring them for 