ism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"In May 2021, we made a decision to change our lawn service provider. As part of that change, it was necessary to replace a substantial portion of our lawn. The new sections of the lawn have been put down to our total satisfaction. We give the highest possible thanks to Justin and the rest of the crew involved in this project . They were most helpful with their ideas and patient with us throughout this process. In addition to the outcome of this project , we would like to give positive recognition to the maintenance crew that does our weekly work. They do it right. Changing to the Michaelangelo\'s Group has been one of our best decisions in 2021. We look forward to a long lasting relationship with them.","likes":1,"response":{"date":"8 months ago","snippet":"Joann, we appreciate the compliment!"}},{"user":{"name":"Michael Bridge","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/107034748842805174428?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiTqP_Vxrj3AhWTlWoFHYnnBhsQvvQBegUIARCUAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJzzwHCwv2Aet-1r1D1EAw8CmaMfS4O-aQBa1A-c=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":2},"rating":1,"date":"3 weeks ago","snippet":"Filled out the online form requesting a general estimate for some backyard retaining walls, stone slab steps, updated drainage, perhaps some paver stone sidewalks\u2026 this is the copy\/pasted response: \u201cOur process is to book you for a consultation through Zoom, just for us to have a deeper understanding of your project , we can find out your goal and make recommendations moving forward, then step two is a design consultation, we\'ll schedule our landscape architect to visit your property and create a design for you, we will provide you an estimate based on the design. Our design fee is based on $125.00 per hour for the consultation and plan preparation time while the cost of plans ranges from $600 - $800, on top of that, we have a minimum of $20,000 for a project .\u201d Zero mention of these minimums on the website, and why would we require a designer or landscape architect to replace\/repair what already exists? Nothing about the design needs altered\u2026just rebuild with new manufactured stone and update the existing irrigation system with new. 15 stone steps where steps already exist\u2026easy, right? It\u2019s just fine if you only want to cater to higher end projects , but make that known on your webpage. I guess a $10K - $15k budget isn\u2019t worthy of this Company\u2019s attention? Sorry to waste both of our time."},{"user":{"name":"Teri Tang","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/107492841921640462486?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiTqP_Vxrj3AhWTlWoFHYnnBhsQvvQBegUIARChAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJw7WqePfj7x5VMpVU6xl49UOGC-kmczI4RfadSm=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":2,"photos":3},"rating":5,"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Michaelangelo\u2019s created this magnificent fireplace as well as did the landscaping that surrounds it. Michael was there with us every step of the way! We couldn\u2019t be happier with the ENTIRE experience! Juan and his crew at Michaelangelo\u2019s were so attentive to our wants and needs for our project . Bruce was AMAZING with the details on the blueprint he provided us for the landscaping. If you are looking for a company that truly stands behind their work before, during, and after the sale, look to Michaelangelo\u2019s!","likes":1,"images":["https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/p\/AF1QipPLlwU7_crEz6wO6PFa3NA5XPhv_reky6pGOrKU=w100-h100-p-n-k-no","https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/p\/AF1QipPeY9rlKxfcKNDxMGbVoVnb1MpCKW0s7I3OiRvl=w100-h100-p-n-k-no","https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/p\/AF1QipNIxBLnf28oTE884HoYjKN0YZKzyDbY_NXiT-l_=w100-h100-p-n-k-no"],"response":{"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Thank you so much for the amazing review. We plan to enter your project for an award later this year. Stay tuned!"}},{"user":{"name"