s accommodated. There was considerable \'clean up\' of our landscape due to construction. The team lead JC and crew did a great job of removing all the debris and stacking remaining brick and flagstone neatly in location of our choosing. I would certainly recommend them and would use them again.","likes":1,"images":["https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/p\/AF1QipO_EiQUIzFKENLtuG51Zz_UTnTc1_ann7W9pqQa=w100-h100-p-n-k-no"],"response":{"date":"a year ago","snippet":"Thank you for the kind feedback, John!"}},{"user":{"name":"Jian Griffin","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/112782462460325258283?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiTqP_Vxrj3AhWTlWoFHYnnBhsQvvQBegUIARDTAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJw5piO3vJuEhUMMOK-BV9ZwlK2bVHR7WV7T0oj7=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":1},"rating":5,"date":"7 months ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness","snippet":"The scope of our backyard project included expanding our exiting covered patio, building a stone sitting wall along with the firepit as well as redesigning the backyard landscaping. We consulted numerous landscaping companies to provide the estimate. Ultimately we chose Michelangelo Landscaping due to its sustainable design proposal, the smooth transition\/correlation to our existing landscaping structure, and the last but not least, the honest and upfront communication throughout the process. Very happy with the end presentation and look forward to working with you guys in the future. Services: Custom masonry , Stone masonry","likes":1,"response":{"date":"7 months ago","snippet":"Thank you for the kind feedback, Jian!"}},{"user":{"name":"Barbara Mcaloon","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/105331050284769582290?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjqps3Yxrj3AhVRpnIEHVHpBBUQvvQBegQIARBB","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJxVYvzzJFLDTsFKI75Ov3k_P1oLey2PggZF3bRA=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":2,"photos":2