ick and flagstone neatly in location of our choosing. I would certainly recommend them and would use them again.","likes":1,"images":["https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/p\/AF1QipO_EiQUIzFKENLtuG51Zz_UTnTc1_ann7W9pqQa=w100-h100-p-n-k-no"],"response":{"date":"a year ago","snippet":"Thank you for the kind feedback, John!"}},{"user":{"name":"Robert Colliersmith","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/102413945022809740243?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjqps3Yxrj3AhVRpnIEHVHpBBUQvvQBegQIARBk","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJxzXJ0MVeHlSuKR9zSZoYeqaTd6giiQwjhHL6su=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":4},"rating":5,"date":"a year ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"I was quite pleased with the service and work done by Michaelangelo\'s. The crew showed up on the date and time assigned and were ready to go. They worked continuously until the work had been completed, pausing only to confirm with me how I wanted the landscaping to be done and how I wanted it to look when they had completed the job . They were courteous and efficient. Everything went smoothly and without problem. I would have no reservation about using them again if or when the need should arise. Five Stars.","likes":4,"response":{"date":"a year ago","snippet":"Thank you Robert. We were glad to help you with your home. Please let us know if there is any issues with the Fescue seed, as we would be glad to come back and apply some more."}},{"user":{"name":"scott rooks","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/101190692087264787535?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjqps3Yxrj3AhVRpnIEHVHpBBUQvvQBegQIARBz","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a-\/AOh14GiYxGLFONmuJfh6VMWDmRjwm2fEkoJXtWptSvFDXw=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4-br100","local_guide":true,"reviews":176,"photos":148},"rating":5,"date":"2 years ago","snippet":"They did a great job. Everything I asked for was taken care of and they kept me in the