Miotke","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/103848078550460347575?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjqps3Yxrj3AhVRpnIEHVHpBBUQvvQBegUIARCPAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a-\/AOh14Gh1VxM1ziQVqHtq51rzyXE2-fn2opwrJBSh4hiCvg=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":4},"rating":5,"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Michael\'s team is quick professional and did a great job . I have hired him twice. Once to do a patio. It was sinking and they leveled it out. No problems at all a year later. The second time was to level the backyard so there was no potholes or puddles when it rained and pull up a couple dead trees. I thought it would take a week and it took two days. Everyone wore uniforms and they were on time, quick and efficient. I would always hire Michael now and always recommend him for landscaping needs.","likes":1,"response":{"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Thank you for your great review, Jennifer! We feel it\'s important to maintain a professional image for all of our jobs. Thanks for noticing! We\'re happy to hear you\'ve had a great experience with us! Thank you for choosing Michaelangelo\'s Sustainable Landscape & Design Group!"}},{"user":{"name":"Joe Sapere","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/116706218097439044170?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjqps3Yxrj3AhVRpnIEHVHpBBUQvvQBegUIARCbAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJz0R2DysorwF1U3Monku9bOsJthdN1hrwEf9LH_=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4-br100","local_guide":true,"reviews":88,"photos":4},"rating":5,"date":"2 years ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"WHAT WE HAD DONE - Residential Landscaping (Drainage, Re-Sod, Clean-up, Tree Removal) Drainage We\'ve had drainage issues for years because of where our house sits on a street at the bottom of a hill. They fixed this, regraded the soil, and installed new sod for our entire yard. Several days later, we had an hours-long downpour and no puddles or mud. It\'s actually hard to believe that our yard has no issues after all that rain. Concrete Ext. & Garden Box We had concrete extended on our back porch. They also built a terraced garden box with gardening soil. It\'s my favorite part of the yard. It\'s well-constructed and just a beautiful addition to our lawn. These guys do phenomenal work. I just can\'t get over how good it looks. I couldn\'t have done this myself nor could anyone on the cheap. It took professionals who knew what they\'re doing and worked as a team to produce these results. It probably helps that Michael is a landscape architect who oversees every job , not everyone is a landscape architect. They are more expensive but you get your money\'s worth and their work is guaranteed for a year. Looking back, I still would not have gone with any of the cheaper alternatives. I don\'t have a lot of money but I also don\'t have the time, patience, or money to deal with work that isn\'t done quite right and dealing with all that. If you want to take the risk and pay less for someone else, you can do that. But if you want value, what you get for what you pay for, and guaranteed to be done right, Michaelangelo\'s is who you\'ll want for this work.","likes":1,"response":{"date":"a year ago","snippet":"Thanks Joe!"}},{"user":{"name":"Susan K","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/101237316135648039892?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjqps3Yxrj3AhVRpnIEHVHpBBUQvvQBegUIARCqAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a-\/AOh14GiZsHdUdjnal5QExXkk0Jyr1oE5Z9mToXcMhAEBLA=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":6},"rating":5,"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Michaelangelo\'s was referred to me by a neighbor and I\'m so glad that I followed up on her recommendation. Michael was very knowledgeable about landscaping and listened to my needs and concerns. The crew was on time and, even though the job turned out to be more than they anticipated, completed it the same day as promised. They even provided me with maintenance information for my new lawn and tree. I\'ll definitely call them when I\'m ready to do the back yard!","likes":1,"response":{"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Thank you so much for the review. We really enjoyed working with you!"}},{"user":{"name":"Bill Daniel Daniel","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/117759681069139964165?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjqps3Yxrj3AhVRpnIEHVHpBBUQvvQBegUIARC2AQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJzeUN6Mb76xiqpn8chzFbFTfVU4BU0aZys1X9hF=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":1},"rating":5,"date":"4 years ago","snippet":"Everyone with this company worked their tails off. They were all courteous and friendly, and genuinely enjoyed their work. They stayed on schedule, and finished on time, and they did a fabulous job with a complete new irrigation and sprinkler system, boulder removal, graded the entire yard, laid 20 pallets of new zenith zoysia, and 100 bales of pinestraw.","response":{"date":"4 years ago","snippet":"We really appreciate the opportunity to serve you! You were very pleasant to work with. Please tell your friends and family about our wonderful service!"}},{"user":{"name":"Mike Bober","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/101166961101008050988?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjqps3Yxrj3AhVRpnIEHVHpBBUQvvQBegUIARDCAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJy8xkBiLyHKe-zxIJ_QXt3InNvAIlcz4HqPM8ro=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":1},"rating":5,"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Michaelangelo\'s Landscape did a great job on my storm drainage problem. They were on time, professional, and did my job for a fair price. I would definitely recommend them.","likes":1,"response":{"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Thank you for the recommendation, Mike!"}},{"user":{"name":"Jill Oliver","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/110507678121485836512?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjZjJHbxrj3AhU9mHIEHbG2BgoQvvQBegQIARBB","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/