nd helpful to get the right plants and keep the project rolling. Edwin, Mario, and Carlos are extremely an amazing team. We have never seen a team that work so hard and efficient as these trio. They are always happy to answer all my questions and concerns. They are so sweet and sincere. Mario really goes above and beyond to make this project a success. We have been waiting to have a beautiful backyard for years. Thanks to this AMAZING team for making this happen. Service: Custom masonry","likes":2,"response":{"date":"4 months ago","snippet":"Thank you for the kind feedback, Ni!"}},{"user":{"name":"Michael Bridge","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/107034748842805174428?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjZjJHbxrj3AhU9mHIEHbG2BgoQvvQBegQIARBo","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJzzwHCwv2Aet-1r1D1EAw8CmaMfS4O-aQBa1A-c=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":2},"rating":1,"date":"3 weeks ago","snippet":"Filled out the online form requesting a general estimate for some backyard retaining walls, stone slab steps, updated drainage, perhaps some paver stone sidewalks\u2026 this is the copy\/pasted response: \u201cOur process is to book you for a consultation through Zoom, just for us to have a deeper understanding of your project, we can find out your goal and make recommendations moving forward, then step two is a design consultation, we\'ll schedule our landscape architect to visit your property and create a design for you, we will provide you an estimate based on the design. Our design fee is based on $125.00 per hour for the consultation and plan preparation time while the cost of plans ranges from $600 - $800, on top of that, we have a minimum of $20,000 for a project.\u201d Zero mention of these minimums on the website, and why would we require a designer or landscape architect to replace\/repair what already exists? Nothing about the design needs altered\u2026just rebuild with new manufactured stone and update the existing irrigation system with new. 15 stone steps where steps already exist\u2026easy, right? It\u2019s just fine if you only want to cater to higher end projects, but make that known on your webpage. I guess a $10K - $15k budget isn\u2019t worthy of this Company\u2019s attention? Sorry to waste both of our time."},{"user":{"name":"Jian Griffin","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/112782462460325258283?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjZjJHbxrj3AhU9mHIEHbG2BgoQvvQBegQIARB1","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJw5piO3vJuEhUMMOK-BV9ZwlK2bVHR7WV7T0oj7=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":1},"rating":5,"date":"7 months ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness","snippet":"The scope of our backyard project included expanding our exiting covered patio, building a stone sitting wall along with the firepit as well as redesigning the backyard landscaping. We consulted numerous landscaping companies to provide the estimate. Ultimately we chose Michelangelo Landscaping due to its sustainable design proposal, the smooth transition\/correlation to our existing landscaping structure, and the last but not least, the honest and upfront communication throughout the process. Very happy with the end presentation and look forward to working with you guys in the future. Services: Custom masonry , Stone masonry","likes":1,"response":{"date":"7 months ago","snippet":"Thank you for the kind feedback, Jian!"}},{"user":{"name":"Veronica Gomes","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/103152089037287844675?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjZjJHbxrj3AhU9mHIEHbG2BgoQvvQBegUIARCHAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a-\/AOh14GgBN41XC2QYBjaI_9MO74N3-MhjYakyyxX1rbPQ=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":2},"rating":5,"date":"9 months ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"We had them redo our back yard from scratch. Eugene and the rest of the team were great! They 