faction. We give the highest possible thanks to Justin and the rest of the crew involved in this project. They were most helpful with their ideas and patient with us throughout this process. In addition to the outcome of this project, we would like to give positive recognition to the maintenance crew that does our weekly work. They do it right. Changing to the Michaelangelo\'s Group has been one of our best decisions in 2021. We look forward to a long lasting relationship with them.","likes":1,"response":{"date":"8 months ago","snippet":"Joann, we appreciate the compliment!"}},{"user":{"name":"Steven Rankin","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/108035053428023297010?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj-7N3bxrj3AhWIgnIEHXZdCQIQvvQBegQIARBm","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJxKRX8pg0VpQldYyJ-7cm-AoebrFRHgg2XlHdJq=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":5,"photos":1},"rating":5,"date":"4 months ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality","snippet":"They were able to start slightly ahead of schedule due to changes in other jobs, contacted me and kept me inform of the schedule changes. They finished that same amount of time early, so job was estimated appropriately with time and budget. Crew worked a full normal day each day and job looks wonderful. Update***I\'ve been using the fertilization service since the masonry work was done this spring. My original landscaping crew kept scalping my yard and I decided to take over the maintenance. Michelangelo\'s guy comes out 9-10x per year and analysis my yard and fertilizes\/weeds appropriately. My yard looks better now in December than it did in May! Growing so thick and still beautiful green. They are top notch and VERY INEXPENSIVE for the professionalism and great work you\'ll receive. Service: Stone masonry","likes":2,"response":{"date":"10 months ago","snippet":"Thank you! Please let us know how we could assist you in the future."}},{"user":{"name":"Teri Tang","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/107492841921640462486?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj-7N3bxrj3AhWIgnIEHXZdCQIQvvQBegQIARB3","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJw7WqePfj7x5VMpVU6xl49UOGC-kmczI4RfadSm=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":2,"photos":3},"rating":5,"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Michaelangelo\u2019s created this magnificent fireplace as well as did the landscaping that surrounds it. Michael was there with us every step of the way! We couldn\u2019t be happier with the ENTIRE experience! Juan and his crew at Michaelangelo\u2019s were so attentive to our wants and needs for our project. Bruce was AMAZING with the details on the blueprint he provided us for the landscaping. If you are looking for a company that truly stands behind their work before, during, and after the sale, look to Michaelangelo\u2019s!","likes":1,"images":["https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/p\/AF1QipPLlwU7_crEz6wO6PFa3NA5XPhv_reky6pGOrKU=w100-h100-p-n-k-no","https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/p\/AF1QipPeY9rlKxfcKNDxMGbVoVnb1MpCKW0s7I3OiRvl=w100-h100-p-n-k-no","https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/p\/AF1QipNIxBLnf28oTE884HoYjKN0YZKzyDbY_NXiT-l_=w100-h100-p-n-k-no"],"response":{"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Thank you so much for the amazing review. We plan to enter your project for an award later this year. Stay tuned!"}},{"user":{"name":"John Swartz","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/113601031643881943186?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj-7N3bxrj3AhWIgnIEHXZdCQIQvvQBegUIARCHAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJxtTHqFCXoBZiAmHEacPXpggxGaAL8MgnCuAPdK=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":5,"photos":1},"rating":5,"date":"a year ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness","snippet":"Michael visit twice before our decision. On both occasions he was attentive and listened to what we wanted. He made suggestions but never tried to forced those suggestions into the contract. His team