nt. They blew everything including our front and back decks so it looked amazing. We have a parking spot which always flooded after a rain. Michael said to just lower the surrounding landscaping. Since it is now covered with plantings and mulch, the water drains beautifully and it doesn\'t even look like there was ever a problem. We highly recommend Michaelangelo\'s for their creative design work, their excellent implementation of the perfect plan for our home and their professionalism throughout!","likes":3,"response":{"date":"a year ago","snippet":"Ellen thank you so much for trusting us and coming back to us even 3 years after the original design! We are glad you are happy and now your house will be ready to sell, problem free!"}},{"user":{"name":"Robert Colliersmith","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/102413945022809740243?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj-7N3bxrj3AhWIgnIEHXZdCQIQvvQBegUIARCnAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJxzXJ0MVeHlSuKR9zSZoYeqaTd6giiQwjhHL6su=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":4},"rating":5,"date":"a year ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"I was quite pleased with the service and work done by Michaelangelo\'s. The crew showed up on the date and time assigned and were ready to go. They worked continuously until the work had been completed, pausing only to confirm with me how I wanted the landscaping to be done and how I wanted it to look when they had completed the job. They were courteous and efficient. Everything went smoothly and without problem. I would have no reservation about using them again if or when the need should arise. Five Stars.","likes":4,"response":{"date":"a year ago","snippet":"Thank you Robert. We were glad to help you with your home. Please let us know if there is any issues with the Fescue seed, as we would be glad to come back and apply some more."}},{"user":{"name":"Susan K","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/ma