te the compliment!"}},{"user":{"name":"Sally Ann Lopez","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/106912505942270255688?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiJ7qvcxrj3AhXNg3IEHc8iA2kQvvQBegUIARCOAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJyrPfjrprprUBl0-lnhmC3orsE0tx2W_ZebtH6m=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":5},"rating":5,"date":"2 years ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"I chose Michaelangelo\'s for a landscaping and hardscaping project to add tiered garden beds to my sloped yard along with pollinator plants and shrubs to create a garden space. From the outset, I really appreciated Michael\'s attention to the sustainability and aesthetic aspect. He recommended going with boulders rather than wood- which is more long-lasting, sustainable, cost-effective and beautiful. His team was incredibly professional and worked side by side with me as I have very particular taste and requirements. I really appreciated how much they cared in how I was feeling throughout the whole process and they regularly checked in to make sure everything was to my taste. I would definitely recommend them and plan to use them again in future projects.","response":{"date":"a year ago","snippet":"We take pride in knowing we met your expectations!"}},{"user":{"name":"Joseph Campbell","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/114196083197945593388?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiJ7qvcxrj3AhXNg3IEHc8iA2kQvvQBegUIARCdAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJziGG0KGC2o6vGYxSRkrt4maA6CdlSCMrY6EGXfww=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":1},"rating":3,"date":"10 months ago","snippet":"Summary: Higher priced than others for the same scope of work, quality of plants they used seem to be of lower cost- perhaps to cut corners and increase margin. The value is questionable. We water regularly and according to their directions. After 1 month, we needed a few plants to be replaced under their 