you! Please let us know how we could assist you in the future."}},{"user":{"name":"Joann Rison","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/107279145454198530507?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjC9a7exrj3AhWNpXIEHSN0DkIQvvQBegQIARBQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJzcEQXe-IdSWXIvT1uDcU5U9VZYtzNbo-0ChAVB=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":2},"rating":5,"date":"8 months ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"In May 2021, we made a decision to change our lawn service provider. As part of that change, it was necessary to replace a substantial portion of our lawn . The new sections of the lawn have been put down to our total satisfaction. We give the highest possible thanks to Justin and the rest of the crew involved in this project. They were most helpful with their ideas and patient with us throughout this process. In addition to the outcome of this project, we would like to give positive recognition to the maintenance crew that does our weekly work. They do it right. Changing to the Michaelangelo\'s Group has been one of our best decisions in 2021. We look forward to a long lasting relationship with them.","likes":1,"response":{"date":"8 months ago","snippet":"Joann, we appreciate the compliment!"}},{"user":{"name":"Felicia McCall","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/105775341213997625171?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjC9a7exrj3AhWNpXIEHSN0DkIQvvQBegQIARBf","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a-\/AOh14GhsuRoln32-C34g_k4BkfExQUjrwgYW34wYEeVugAw=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":4,"photos":2},"rating":5,"date":"3 months ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness, ValuePancho quickly identified my issue and turned my lawn around in just a few weeks. I am amazed at the results. Ask for Pancho!","likes":1,"images":["https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/p\/AF1QipMi7iWm7URrxLvEvg-Sz9F0-6G1ULKQA_5gXi3I=w100-h100-p-n-k-no","https:\/\/lh5.googleusercontent.com\/p\/AF1QipP8Qvlx1yKxnav-h8T0UxLwDpn2uyl-iMxXIaIx=w100-h100-p-n-k-no"],"response":{"date":"3 months ago","snippet":"Thank you for the kind feedback, Felicia!"}},{"user":{"name":"Jeff Harold","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/106413282829587246146?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjC9a7exrj3AhWNpXIEHSN0DkIQvvQBegQIARBw","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a-\/AOh14GiuYB1i107x9836DCJKJEqvGbgoM0wTkmiJpUkY=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":5},"rating":1,"date":"10 months ago","summary":"Critical: Quality, Responsiveness","snippet":"Left my yard a mess and never finished to my satisfaction. My mistake for being on a conf call when they wrapped up. Would not recommend. ------------------------------ Specifically, the small paver path is still not laid properly (done twice), I was told the straw that was placed after the project contained grass seed, as grass has not grown, I believe that statement was untrue, under the straw is a rocky\/bumpy mess and should have been rolled flat, as it was before the work was done, pee gravel was spilled in the yard and it remains. I had to redo the entire long paver path that was damaged and knocked out of alignment by the equipment. As I said, my bad for being on a conf call when I paid. I don\'t expect anything else from your company, I simple was replying to a request for a review.","likes":1,"response":{"date":"8 months ago","snippet":"Thank you for your feedback, Jeff. We are concerned to hear you feel this way about your experience, as we returned to your property several times to make adjustments and your project was paid in full 100%. From our perspective, we did everything we could to ensure your satisfaction. Our before and after pictures of the project show that your yard was properly cleaned up after the final touches were complete, so we\u2019re not sure why you feel the yard was left a mess. Please feel free to contact us if there are any further specifics you\u2019d like to provide. Thank you. Michael"}},{"user":{"name":"Joe Sapere","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/116706218097439044170?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjC9a7exrj3AhWNpXIEHSN0DkIQvvQBegQIARB_","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJz0R2DysorwF1U3Monku9bOsJthdN1hrwEf9LH_=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4-br100","local_guide":true,"reviews":88,"photos":4},"rating":5,"date":"2 years ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Quality, Responsiveness, Value","snippet":"WHAT WE HAD DONE - Residential Landscaping (Drainage, Re-Sod, Clean-up, Tree Removal) Drainage We\'ve had drainage issues for years because of where our house sits on a street at the bottom of a hill. They fixed this, regraded the soil, and installed new sod for our entire yard. Several days later, we had an hours-long downpour and no puddles or mud. It\'s actually hard to believe that our yard has no issues after all that rain. Concrete Ext. & Garden Box We had concrete extended on our back porch. They also built a terraced garden box with gardening soil. It\'s my favorite part of the yard. It\'s well-constructed and just a beautiful addition to our lawn . These guys do phenomenal work. I just can\'t get over how good it looks. I couldn\'t have done this myself nor could anyone on the cheap. It took professionals who knew what they\'re doing and worked as a team to produce these results. It probably helps that Michael is a landscape architect who oversees every job, not everyone is a landscape architect. They are more expensive but you get your money\'s worth and their work is guaranteed for a year. Looking back, I still would not have gone with any of the cheaper alternatives. I don\'t have a lot of money but I also don\'t have the time, patience, or money to deal with work that isn\'t done quite right and dealing with all that. If you want to take the risk and pay less for someone else, you can do that. But if you want value, what you get for what you pay for, and guaranteed to be done right, Michaelangelo\'s is who you\'ll want for this work.","likes":1,"response":{"date":"a year ago","snippet":"Thanks Joe!"}},{"user":{"name":"Susan K","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/101237316135648039892?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjC9a7exrj3AhWNpXIEHSN0DkIQvvQBegUIARCOAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a-\/AOh14GiZsHdUdjnal5QExXkk0Jyr1oE5Z9mToXcMhAEBLA=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":6},"rating":5,"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Michaelangelo\'s was referred to me by a neighbor and I\'m so glad that I followed up on her recommendation. Michael was very knowledgeable about landscaping and listened to my needs and concerns. The crew was on time and, even though the job turned out to be more than they anticipated, completed it the same day as promised. They even provided me with maintenance information for my new lawn and tree. I\'ll definitely call them when I\'m ready to do the back yard!","likes":1,"response":{"date":"3 years ago","snippet":"Thank you so much for the review. We really enjoyed working with you!"}},{"user":{"name":"Tanya B","link":"https:\/\/www.google.com\/maps\/contrib\/103289933338280638564?hl=en-US&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjC9a7exrj3AhWNpXIEHSN0DkIQvvQBegUIARCaAQ","thumbnail":"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/a\/AATXAJy3e3QIBMrwjyc5i0kzUw6T9GQyJxMyl6ztqKvo=s40-c-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-br100","reviews":5},"rating":5,"date":"10 months ago","summary":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, Responsiveness","snippet":"Positive: Professionalism, Punctuality, Quality, ResponsivenessThis is a great landscaping company to work with. Their quality of work is outstanding. They are responsive, on time, and professional. I use them for all my lawn maintenance.","response":{"date":"10 months ago","snippet":"Tanya, we appreciate the compliment!"}},{"user":{"name":"Joann Rison","link":"https:\/\/www.go